name: Spectre - Ronin
description:
Spectre - Ronin

Spectres origin is unknown. They have been traveling through space and time before those concepts were even conceived. 
With their trusty sprite "Glitch" a hybrid mechanical organic being from Zeta Terra 3, they travel together exploring, observing and documenting.

This is the next piece in the series of exploration and discovery in different art styles.
